ation that helps provide equitable quality of care for all Manitobans? ","index":"00254","speaker":""},{"html":"<b><span lang=\"FR-CA\">Hon. Rochelle </span></b><b><a name=\"_Toc21700414\"><span lang=\"FR-CA\">Squires</span></a></b><b><span lang=\"FR-CA\">�(Minister responsible for Francophone Affairs):</span></b><span lang=\"FR-CA\"> Merci beaucoup, Madame la Pr�sidente, pour la question. Notre\ngouvernement va continuer � soutenir les services francophones au Manitoba. </span>","index":"00255","speaker":"Rochelle Squires"},{"html":"<b><i>Translation</i></b>","index":"00256","speaker":""},{"html":"<i>Thank you very much, Madam Speaker, for the question. Our government\nwill continue to support French language services in Manitoba. </i>�","index":"00257","speaker":""},{"html":"<b><i>English</i></b>","index":"00258","speaker":""},{"html":"����� We're very proud to continue to stand up for francophones in the\nprovince of Manitoba making good investments. We just signed the\nCanada-Manitoba Agreement on French Language Services to provide benefits for\ncommunity service organizations and help in getting good positive outcomes\nwhether it be in health, social services or many other areas of the community\nthat require services in French. ","index":"00259","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Madam Speaker:</b> The honourable member for St.&nbsp;James, on a\nsupplementary question.","index":"00260","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Mr. Adrien </b><b><a name=\"_Toc21700416\">Sala</a></b><b>�(St. James):</b> French language services keep undergoing cut after\ncut under this government. The francophone community does not forget that this\ngovernment cut the assistant deputy minister role from the bureau d'�ducation\nfran�aise. ","index":"00261","speaker":"Adrien Sala"},{"html":"����� The minister isn't listening to what the community is saying and\nis allowing this�<i>[interjection]</i>","index":"00262","speaker":""},{"html":"<b>Madam Speaker:</b> Order. ","index":"00263","speaker":""},{"htm